point annotation with a view object. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method or have it return ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" for that annotation, then implement","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" is an instance of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" (or equal to the map view’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property), return an instance of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(or a subclass thereof)."}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" to use for a given "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" object on your"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map."}]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L742"},"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"View representing an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" on screen.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"title":"MLNUserLocation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" object from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property of the map view displayed in your application."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"}}}